OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779494576
OL,3,CChildren 'more likely than working-age
OL,4,Cadults to live in private rented
OL,5,Csector'
OL,7,FChildren are more likely than working-
OL,8,Fage adults to live in Britain's
OL,9,Fprivate rented sector, as young
OL,10,Ffamilies who may find themselves
OL,11,Fpriced out of homeownership rent for
OL,12,Flonger, according to a think-tank.
OL,14,FThe number of children living in the
OL,15,Fprivate rented sector (PRS) has nearly
OL,16,Ftripled over the last quarter of a
OL,17,Fcentury, from 1.1 million children in
OL,18,F2000-01 to 3.2 million in 2024-25, the
OL,19,FResolution Foundation said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779494576
OL,3,CChildren 'more likely than working-age
OL,4,Cadults to live in private rented
OL,5,Csector'
OL,7,FIt said children are now more likely
OL,8,Fthan working-age adults to live in the
OL,9,Fprivate rented sector, at 23% compared
OL,10,Fwith 22%.
OL,12,FBritain's private rented sector has
OL,13,Fmore than doubled in size since the
OL,14,Fturn of the century, the foundation
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FSome 12.9 million people, living in
OL,18,F5.1 million households, now call it
OL,19,Fhome, compared with 5.1 million
OL,20,Fpeople, in 2.5 million households, in
OL,21,F2000-01.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779494576
OL,3,CChildren 'more likely than working-age
OL,4,Cadults to live in private rented
OL,5,Csector'
OL,7,FAs the number of private renters has
OL,8,Fchanged, so too have the
OL,9,Fcharacteristics of tenants, the
OL,10,Fresearch found.
OL,12,FAlthough those in their 20s are still
OL,13,Fthe most likely age group to be
OL,14,Fprivate tenants (37% in 2024-25), the
OL,15,Fshare of people aged in their 30s in
OL,16,Fthis tenure has nearly trebled, from
OL,17,F10% to 28% between 2000-01 and 2024-25.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
