OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779494576
OL,3,CChildren 'more likely than working-age
OL,4,Cadults to live in private rented
OL,5,Csector'
OL,7,FTenants are also able to challenge
OL,8,Funfair rent hikes.
OL,10,FThe foundation's work focuses
OL,11,Fparticularly on households with low
OL,12,Fand middle incomes, those on low pay
OL,13,For in precarious work, and those who
OL,14,Fare vulnerable to financial shocks.
OL,16,FIt said that, on average, private
OL,17,Frenters in the UK spend around 35% of
OL,18,Ftheir income on housing costs, above
OL,19,Fthe 30% threshold generally considered
OL,20,Faffordable.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
