OL,3,CChildren 'more likely than working-age
OL,4,Cadults to live in private rented
OL,5,Csector'
OL,7,FThe report said: "The impact that rent
OL,8,Fhas on disposable income is
OL,9,Fparticularly severe for those on lower
OL,10,Fincomes who receive help towards their
OL,11,Frent through the benefit system."
OL,13,FHannah Aldridge, a senior research and
OL,14,Fpolicy analyst at the Resolution
OL,15,FFoundation, said: "For a growing
OL,16,Fnumber of people, the private rented
OL,17,Fsector is less a pitstop on the way to
OL,18,Fhome ownership or a social tenancy,
OL,19,Fand more a permanent home.
OL,26,@oD@ROUsD@aO]wD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1779494576
OL,3,CChildren 'more likely than working-age
OL,4,Cadults to live in private rented
OL,5,Csector'
OL,7,F"Children are now more likely to live
OL,8,Fin private rented homes than working-
OL,9,Fage adults, and the number of private
OL,10,Frenters in their 30s has soared as
OL,11,Fyoung families are priced out of
OL,12,Fhomeownership.
OL,14,F"Yet private rented accommodation is
OL,15,Fmore likely to be damp and energy
OL,16,Finefficient than other tenures, and
OL,17,Fmany vulnerable private renters report
OL,18,Ffeeling so insecure in their homes
OL,19,Fthey are unable to make long-term
OL,20,Fdecisions.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
