OL,3,CChildren 'more likely than working-age
OL,4,Cadults to live in private rented
OL,5,Csector'
OL,7,F"We are also restoring the dream of
OL,8,Fhome ownership through a record #39
OL,9,Fbillion investment in social and
OL,10,Faffordable housing ` building the
OL,11,Fhomes this country needs and making
OL,12,Fthem more affordable by boosting
OL,13,Fsupply."
